name: SpaceLanding
description:
In 1969, Armstrong has been landing on the Moon. Now, it's your time, can you succeed landing on the GD02 which is the deepest planet in the universe? How many times could you land? Try Now For Free!

Move Control

W, A, S, D or ↑, ↓, ←, → to control the directions.

Hold Spacebar to use the fuel.

If the fuel is done or the speed is fast, the ship would destroy
